\id 1PE - Akawaio New Testament Translation Project
\h 1 PI'TA
\toc1 Wapiyaro' Kareta Pi'ta Winɨpaino
\toc2 1 Pi'ta
\toc3 1 Pi'ta
\mt2 Wapiyaro' Kareta
\mt1 Pi'ta
\mt2 Winɨpaino
\imt1 Ekamanin
\ip \bk Wapiyaro' Kareta Pi'ta Winɨpaino\bk* usenno'sa' Kʉri'san amʉ' ena', “Papa nanʉmʉ'san ka'pon amʉ'” tukai' tesa'san, iye'ta'nʉ'sa' kon wʉi enu uyepʉ enwo'netʉ winɨkʉi' Eisa Mʉre'pʉ pɨ'. Eke kuru imenukato' ipɨkɨrɨ esi, imenu ennin nan pori'manin pe, kamo ɨsɨ pe tʉkota'mato' kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ e'ne' moronka pɨ' na'ne' nan apurɨto' to' uya wenai. Imenukanin uya tʉnmenuka'pʉ ennin nan emiya'pontɨ wakʉ Sises Kʉrai ekareei pɨ', iyeri'to', iye'mʉ'sa'kato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉuye'to' pɨ' isauro'sa' rʉ'pʉ to' e'ku'to' ke to' repa. Serɨ weyu yau nin si to' uya e'ne' moronkato' tʉuya'nokon anʉnto' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ imoronkato' pe, i'tui'ma apurɨto' tʉuya'nokon pe' esi i'napairon pe tukai' ti'tu kon tukai', mɨrɨpan kon e'mato' oton, “Sises Kʉrai usenpoika weyu a'tai” (1:7).
\ip Ekamʉn yau to' esi koro'tau to' pori'mapɨtʉ tʉuya pokon pe, imenukanin uya tʉnmenuka'pʉ ennin nan apiyontɨ to' uko'manto' pe Kʉrai iwano' ton ka'pon amʉ' pe.
\iot Iyawon Ekamanin
\io1 Ekamanin (1:1-2)
\io1 Papa uya pika'tɨn nɨto' pɨ' emiya'pontɨn (1:3-12)
\io1 Auro'kan wakʉ pe iteseru uko'man nɨto' pe (1:13—2:10)
\io1 Kʉri'san pe e'nɨ tʉrawasooi e'ne' moronka a'tai (2:11—4:19)
\io1 Kʉri'san pe e'nɨ e'to' mɨ pe te'ku'sen pe pʉra mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyapiyo' pe (5:1-11)
\io1 Iu'matʉ (5:12-14)
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Sises Kʉrai ekareei ekamai' enno'sa', Pi'ta, winɨpaino,
\p Iye'ta'nʉ'sa' kon, ka'kʉran amʉ' non awɨron kon Pontas, Kare'siya, Ka'pato'siya, Eisa Mʉre'pʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Pi'tiniya pon kon, Papa nanʉmʉ'san enakan,
\v 2 Papa, Ikʉipʉnʉ nanʉmʉ'san pena rɨ, Ita'kwarʉ e'tʉrawasoma winɨ inkoneka'san wakʉ pe, Sises Kʉrai mʉnʉ e'pasinpasinma ke mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ imaimu awɨron kon pe:
\p Tɨwɨ wakʉ nonkasa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' nesii ɨpiyau'nokon miyarɨ rɨ.
\s1 Papa Apurɨpɨtʉ Nurɨnan Pe E'ku'nɨto' Esi Pɨ'
\p 
\v 3 Apurɨpɨ'to' nesii, Papa, uyepuru kon Sises Kʉrai Kʉipʉnʉ iwano' pe! Eke pe ɨsentu'kena' pe tesi pɨ' urepasa' iya 'nokon emenna' pe entun nɨto' ke nurɨnan e'ku'nɨto' ya' Sises Kʉrai e'mʉ'sa'kasa' terikʉ'pʉ apai poro,
\v 4 Papa nʉkupʉ'pʉ uiwano' kon pe epoto' ya' Epʉn po nenkurunpayai'ne', iyenkɨ'sɨimu'na pʉra, iya'mota pʉra, ima'ta pʉra rɨ iyesi mɨrɨ yau.
\v 5 Apurɨto' auya'nokon poro, Papa meruntɨrʉ uya awapu'tɨ kon epika'tɨn nɨto' uyepʉ pʉ'kʉ pona, iyekonekasa' na'ne' usenpoikan pɨ' pata weyu u'ma'sa' a'tai.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', pori' pe e'tɨ', aka'ne' pe rʉ'kwɨ rɨ tu'kan nɨ i'tupɨ'nɨto' yau ɨyekota'mato' kon pe kuru rɨ iye'sa' e'tane.
\v 7 Serɨ ton e'seposa' Papa apurɨto' auya'nokon—epe'kena' korʉ entaino tʉuma'tasen ti'tusa' rɨ e'tane apo' ke, mɨrɨ entai rɨ Papa apurɨto' auya'nokon esi ti'tusen pe—mɨrɨpan usenpoikasa' e'to' pe i'nairon apurɨpɨtʉ pe, eke pe kuru iku'to' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ inama Sises Kʉrai usenpoika weyu a'tai.
\v 8 Ensa' auya'nokon pʉra rɨ iye'tane, i'nʉnka auya'nokon; ensa' auya'nokon pʉra rɨ iye'tane serɨ pe, apurɨ auya'nokon, mɨrɨ pɨ' si ipan pe pori' pe ɨwesi kon, eke pe rɨ, ekama poken pʉra rɨ,
\v 9 apʉne pʉra Papa apurɨto' epe'pʉ pe iyesi aya'kwarʉ kon epika'tɨto' eporo auya'nokon.
\p 
\v 10 Serɨ si epika'tɨn nɨto' pɨ' pu'kena' amʉ' tʉusauro'san, wakʉ nonkasa' tʉuye'ton pɨ' ɨpiya'nokon, uya iwarinpa'pʉ tʉuta'kwarʉkai' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ti'tui' kuru rɨ.
\v 11 Iwarinpa pɨ' rɨ to' esi'pʉ ɨ'rɨ a'tai iweyu esi, nai kasa iyepʉ tukai', Kʉrai A'kwarʉ to' yau te'sen nekamanʉ, mɨrɨ a'tai isekamasa' rʉ'pʉ pena Kʉrai ekota'mato' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ a'kwa tʉuye'ton ite'ma'pʉ ta' tukai'.
\v 12 To' ena' isenpoika'pʉ tiwano' kon pe tapiyo' kon pe to' esi pen tukai', e'tane ɨmɨrɨ'nokon iwano' pe, to' usaurokʉ a'tai ekamasa' rʉ'pʉ pɨ', kamoro wakʉ itekare ekamanin nan ɨpɨ'nokon winɨ, Wakʉ A'kwarʉ, Epʉn poi enno'sa' winɨ. Inserʉ amʉ' rɨ nɨrɨ enurikʉ serɨ ton ɨnenpai.
\s1 Wakʉ Pe E'tɨ'
\p 
\v 13 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ɨusenuminkato' kon ikonekatɨ' iku'nin pe; ɨiwano' kon pe ɨse'se'tɨtɨ'; ɨye'ku'to' kon pɨ' ekonekatɨ' ipʉ'kʉ pe pʉra, wakʉ nonkasa' pɨ' ɨyena'nokon te'tʉton Sises Kʉrai usenpoika a'tai.
\v 14 Main awɨron kon mʉre amʉ' kasa, ɨri eseru i'sero' kon pe ke'tʉu, i'tu auya'nokon pʉra iyesi a'tai ɨwesi'pʉ kon kasa.
\v 15 E'tane wakʉ pe e'tɨ' tanporo ɨnkupʉnʉ kon yau, kʉrɨ rɨ ɨkɨ'manin kon esi wakʉ pe na'ne' kasa;
\v 16 apʉne pʉra iye'menukasa' uya: “Wakʉ pe e'tɨ', apʉne pʉra wakʉ pe urɨ esi pɨ',”\f + \fr 1:16 \ft Ripaiti'kas 11:44-45; 19:2; 20:7\f* tasa'.
\p 
\v 17 Ikʉipʉnʉ, esa'nin pe si ɨwesi pɨ' ka'pon tʉrawasooi eseru aimenkanin pe te'sen kʉrɨ rɨ tenu yawon ke pʉra, ɨuko'manto' kon weyu enno'tɨ' serɨ yau te'namai' ipɨ' ka'kʉran pe.
\v 18 I'tu auya'nokon nɨ tʉuma'tasen nɨ korʉ mɨrɨ pe pʉra sirʉpa ke ɨmo'kasa' kon pʉra iyesi, itenpʉ'pʉ pe rɨ ɨuko'manto' kon apai atamokori kon piyapai ɨyena'nokon iye'kwɨrɨ'sa' na'ne',
\v 19 e'tane i'nʉnkena' Kʉrai mʉnʉ, karimeru mʉre imaku'pɨ pen mɨrɨ pe pʉra ma'takʉ'pan pen ke.
\v 20 Anʉnsa' kʉrɨ rɨ pena rɨ non ekoneka rawɨrɨ rɨ, e'tane isenpoikasa' iweyu u'matʉ pɨ' ɨiwano' kon pe.
\v 21 Kʉrɨ rɨ poro Papa apurɨ auya'nokon, i'mʉ'sa'kanin nʉ'pʉ iyeri'sa' apai, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eke pe iku'sa' iya. Mɨrɨ pɨ' si apurɨto' auya'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨye'ku'to' kon esi Papa yau.
\p 
\v 22 Serɨ pe si ɨyekorʉkasa' kon i'napairon awɨrɨ ɨwesi kon winɨ, i'nai rɨ ɨtonpa kon i'nʉnkanin pe ɨwesi kon pa, ɨsi'nʉnkatɨ' ipan pe, tanporo ɨyewan kon pokon pe.\f + \fr 1:22 \ft Tʉron nɨ imenukasa' ton uya, \fq wakʉ ɨyewan kon apai \ft ta.\f*
\v 23 Apʉne pʉra ɨyentuka'sa' kon kanan, tʉuma'tasen itena'pɨ apai pen e'tane tʉuma'tasen pen apai, tɨwɨro' rɨ tʉuko'mansen Papa Maimu poro.
\v 24 Apʉne pʉra,
\q1 “Tanporo ka'pon amʉ' esi wana' kasa,
\q2 tanporo eke pe iku'to' esi pata ipʉrʉ kasa;
\q1 wana' esi taipʉtasen mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pata ipʉrʉ pe te'sen uta'pokʉ,
\q2 
\v 25 e'tane Itepuru Maimu esi tɨwɨro' rɨ,”\f + \fr 1:25 \ft Aisaya 40:6-8\f*
\m tasa'. Serɨ serɨ itekare ɨpɨ'nokon isekamasa' rʉ'pʉ.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', ɨri pe e'pai e'nɨto', enku'tɨnin pe e'nɨto', wakʉ pe e'ku'nɨto', ɨkɨntan nɨto', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tanporo rɨ ɨri pe ka'pon pɨ' usauro'nɨto' inonkatɨ'.
\v 2 Mʉre amʉ' emen entusanon kasa esukenan iya'kwarʉ merʉ' i'se e'tɨ', ɨusemo'ka kon pa ɨyepika'tɨto' kon yau,
\v 3 serɨ si onpasa' auya'nokon Itepuru esi wakʉ pe tukai'.\x - \xo 2:3 \xt Eren 32:8\x*
\s1 Nurɨnan Tɨ' Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Anʉnsa' Kon Ka'pon Amʉ'
\p 
\v 4 Ɨuyepʉ kon koro'tau ipiya', Nurɨnan Tɨ' kasa te'sen—ka'pon amʉ' newaruma'tɨ'pʉ, e'tane Papa uya anʉnsa' i'nʉnkena' pe tʉnkupʉnʉ—
\v 5 ɨmɨrɨ'nokon nɨ nɨrɨ esi nurɨnan tɨ' kasa, to' namɨ'pʉ ita'kwarʉ ɨutɨ pe, wakʉ pe te'san, use'man nɨto' tʉrawasomanin ye' pe rɨ, ɨntʉrʉnʉ use'man nɨto' esi ita'kwarʉ yau Papa nanʉmʉnʉ pe rɨ, Sises Kʉrai poro rɨ.
\v 6 Itekare iye'menukasa' uya ta:
\q1 “Entɨ', tɨ' tʉsa' uya Sayan po,
\q2 anʉnsa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'nʉnkena' itekun airon tɨ',
\q1 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ kʉrɨ apurɨnin
\q2 e'tʉrʉ pʉra iyesi mɨrɨ epiyɨ'nɨto' ya',”\f + \fr 2:6 \ft Aisaya 28:16\f*
\m tasa'.
\v 7 Serɨ si, ɨmɨrɨ'nokon apurɨnin nan pona, tɨ' esi i'nʉnkena' pe, e'tane kamoro apurɨnin nan pen pona,
\q1 “Tɨ', amɨnin nan newaruma'tɨ'pʉ
\q2 ena'pʉ itekun airon pe,”\f + \fr 2:7 \ft Eren 118:22\f*
\m tasa',
\v 8 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ,
\q1 “Tɨ' ka'pon amʉ' e'pi'poto' ipona,
\q2 tɨ' to' uta'mo'kato' pe rɨ iku'nin,”\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Aisaya 8:14\f*
\m tasa'. To' e'pi'po apʉne pʉra itekare awɨrɨ pʉra to' esi pɨ'—mɨrɨto' pe rɨ nɨrɨ to' esi'pʉ.
\p 
\v 9 E'tane ɨmɨrɨ'nokon kamoro anʉnsa' kon ka'pon amʉ', kin iwano' pe use'man nɨto' tʉrawasomanin nan pe, wakʉ tʉpataron kon, ka'pon amʉ' Papa iwano' ton, ekamanin pe ɨwesi kon apurɨpɨ'to' auya'nokon ɨkɨ'manin nʉ'pʉ kon ewarupɨ apai wakʉ rɨ tʉweyu ya'.
\v 10 Pena Papa munkɨ amʉ' pe pʉra rɨ ɨwesi'pʉ kon, e'tane serɨ pe si imunkɨ amʉ' pe me'atʉi'; pena usentu'man nɨto' anʉnsa' auya'nokon pʉra iyesi'pʉ, e'tane serɨ pe si usentu'man nɨto' anʉnsa' auya'nokon man.
\p 
\v 11 Utonpa ton nʉ'kwɨ, ɨyekama'po uya 'nokon ɨnnon kon, ka'kʉran amʉ' pe te'san serɨ non po, ɨsi'nʉmatɨ' ɨri eseru i'se ɨwe'to' kon apai, aya'kwarʉ kon ewa'noma pɨ' na'ne'.
\v 12 Papa apurɨnin nan pen koro'tau wakʉ pe ɨko'mantɨ', to' uya rɨ ɨyeseru'tɨtane'nokon iye'to' pe pʉra rɨ ikupʉ auya'nokon tukai', to' uya wakʉ ɨyeseru kon ento' pe, mɨrɨpan a'kwa eke kuru Papa meruntɨrʉ apurɨpɨ'to' pe to' uya iye'sa' uyense'na'nokon a'tai.
\s1 E'tʉn Nɨto' Pata Esanon Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Esanon Ena'
\p 
\v 13 E'tʉtɨ', Itepuru esi pɨ' rɨ, tanporon kon itepuru ton ena' ka'pon amʉ' koro'tau anʉnsa' kon: kin ena' rɨ, eke kuru itepuru pe;
\v 14 mɨrɨ pe pʉra kopʉna amʉ' rɨ, inennoko'san kamoro ekamʉn ku'nin nʉ'san kota'mai', kamoro iye'to' pe iku'nin nʉ'san apurɨpɨtʉi'ma.
\v 15 Apʉne pʉra Papa eseru rɨ mɨrɨ wakʉ kupʉ winɨ i'tui'ma pʉra iya'kwarʉ pʉnon kon ka'pon amʉ' usauro'to' e'paka'nʉ'to' auya'nokon.
\v 16 Ɨko'mantɨ' ɨnʉ' enawon kon ka'pon amʉ' pe pʉra, e'tane ɨnʉ' enau pʉra ɨwe'to' kon kʉse'nin, ɨri kupʉ auya'nokon wapu pe; ɨko'mantɨ' rɨken Papa poitorʉ ton pe.
\v 17 Tanporon kon nɨ tʉnamai' e'tɨ': apurɨnin nan ɨtonpa kon amʉ' ti'nʉnkai' e'tɨ', Papa inamatɨ', kin tʉnamai' e'tɨ'.
\p 
\v 18 E'tʉtɨ', poitorʉ ton pʉrata ke te'masan pen, ɨyepuru kon ena', tanporon yau to' nama auya'nokon pe, kamoro wakʉ ton pe na'ne' nan mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉusenuminkasan nɨken pen, e'tane kamoro ɨsɨ pe rɨ nɨrɨ ɨku'nin nan kon.
\v 19 Apʉne pʉra tapurɨpɨ'sen pe ka'pon esi mɨrɨ iwenai pʉra rɨ e'ne' moronkanin pe iyesi yau, apʉne pʉra Papa i'tu tʉuya pɨ' mɨrɨ kasa iyesi.
\v 20 E'tane iwenai apanta'mato' kon eporo auya'nokon yau, iye'to' pen nɨ ku'sa' auya'nokon pɨ' imoronka auya'nokon, ɨ'rɨ eporo auya'nokon? E'tane e'ne' moronka auya'nokon yau, wakʉ kupʉ auya'nokon wenai, imoronkatɨ' rɨ, serɨ pɨ' ayapurɨpɨtʉ kon mɨrɨ Papa piyau.
\v 21 Serɨ pona ɨkɨ'masa' kon mɨrɨ, apʉne pʉra Kʉrai uya e'ne' moronka'pʉ ɨiwano' kon pe, ento' auya'nokon ipɨ' tʉnonkai', ite'ma'pʉ poro ɨutɨ kon pa.
\q1 
\v 22 “Makoi kupʉ'pʉ iya pen nɨ,
\q2 kasi ye' pe iye'to' eporo to' uya pʉra rɨ iyesi'pʉ inta nau,”\f + \fr 2:22 \ft Aisaya 53:9\f*
\m ta.
\v 23 To' uya tʉsapema a'tai, ɨ'rɨ ta iya pʉra iyesi'pʉ to' sapema pe; e'ne' moronka tʉuya a'tai, to' enari'pa'pʉ iya pen nɨ. E'tane ru'ku, iye'tʉrʉ'pʉ iteseru aimenkanin wakʉ pe ena'.
\v 24 Kʉrɨ rɨ uya rɨ umakooi kon arɨ'pʉ tʉpun yau kurusu' po, mɨrɨ kasa si eri'nɨto' pe makoi ya', ipoken e'nɨto' iwano' pe; ari'po'pɨ'sa' pata'pʉ winɨ ɨusepi'tɨsa' kon mɨrɨ.
\v 25 Karimeru utano'ma kasa ɨwesi'pʉ kon, e'tane serɨ pe si ɨyenna'posa' kon aya'kwarʉ kon Esa' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ aya'kwarʉ kon Ennin piya'.
\c 3
\s1 No'pʉ Ton Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Taan'pʉ Ton
\p 
\v 1 No'pʉ ton, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ ataan'pʉ kon ena' e'tʉtɨ', to' tonpa ton uya main apurɨ pʉra iyesi yau, to' ɨ'kwɨrɨ'to' pe apurɨto' winɨkʉi' ɨnkupʉnʉ kon winɨ, ausaurokʉ kon winɨ pen,\x - \xo 3:1 \xt E'pe'sas 5:22; Koro'se 3:18\x*
\v 2 wakʉ pe, Papa tʉnamai' ɨuko'mamʉ kon ene to' uya a'tai.
\v 3 Ayama'nomʉ kon kʉse'nin kɨpo'po rɨ ɨye'rɨwʉntɨsa' kon winɨ, inse' ka'pɨ'sa' pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ korʉ konekasa' rɨ ɨrɨwʉn kon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ ton nɨ ɨpon kon pe.\x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1 Temu'ti 2:9\x*
\v 4 E'tane ru'ku, a'nau'nokon nesii, ama'non pe pʉra tenasen pen ɨ'sɨ'mʉn yai e'nɨto' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉnpan iya'kwarʉ pe, eke kuru itepe' Papa enu yau.
\v 5 Apʉne pʉra serɨ kasa penaro' kon wakʉ ton uri'sami'si amʉ' Papa ena' te'ku'to' kon nonkanin nan enapɨ'pɨtʉ'pʉ ama'non pe. Tʉtaan'pʉ kon ena' te'tʉse to' e'pɨ'pɨtʉ'pʉ,
\v 6 Sera kasa, Epʉra'an maimu awɨron mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tepuru pe esa'nin. Imunkɨ amʉ' ɨmɨrɨ'nokon, ipokena' pe te'sen kupʉ auya'nokon yau, nari' ya' te'tʉse pʉra.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Iseneses 18:12\x*
\p 
\v 7 Taan'pʉ ton, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ tʉusenuminkai' te'san pe e'tɨ' ɨno'pʉ kon pokon pe ɨuko'mamʉ kon koro'tau, to' parɨ tʉnamai' ɨ'sɨ'mʉnon ɨisakon kon pe, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨpokon pe wakʉ uko'man nɨto' epoton kon, ɨ'rɨ uya rɨ ɨwɨpʉremato' kon wa'kʉtʉ namai'.\x - \xo 3:7 \xt E'pe'sas 5:25; Koro'se 3:19\x*
\s1 Ekota'man Wakʉ Kupʉ Wenai
\p 
\v 8 Iye'nonka pe, tanporo ɨmɨrɨ'nokon, ɨsi'kaisa rɨ ɨseseru yau ɨko'mantɨ', ɨtonpa kon pɨ' tʉusenuminkai', ɨsitonpa pe tʉusi'nʉnkai', aiko ta auya'nokon enpoika auya'nokon pe mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ mɨ pe te'ku'san pe pʉra.
\v 9 Ɨri te'mai' pʉra ɨri ke e'tɨ', mɨrɨ pe pʉra e'sapeman, e'sapeman ke, e'tane ɨpʉreman ke, apʉne pʉra serɨ pona ɨkɨ'masa' kon mɨrɨ, Papa uya ɨpʉremato' kon pe.
\v 10 Apʉne pʉra,
\q1 “Ɨnʉ' rɨ uko'man nɨto' i'nʉnkanin,
\q2 wakʉ pe ɨko'manpaino
\q1 tani enkurunpai ɨri apai
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉnta, enku'tɨnin pɨ' isaurokʉ namai'.
\q1 
\v 11 Ɨri apai nera'tɨi wakʉ ku'se'na;
\q2 tʉusewankamai' pʉra e'nɨto' warinpai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iporo te'to' pe.
\q1 
\v 12 Apʉne pʉra Itepuru enu esi ipokena' pe te'san ene pɨ',
\q2 mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipana to' ɨpʉrema eta pɨ',
\q1 e'tane Itepuru emʉ' rɨ ken esi mɨrɨ ɨri ku'nin nan ewa'noma pɨ',”\f + \fr 3:12 \ft Eren 34:12-16\f*
\m tasa'.
\p 
\v 13 Ɨnʉ' uya e'ne' pe ɨkupʉ kon wakʉ ɨnku'pai ɨwesi kon pɨ'?
\v 14 E'tane rɨ ɨyekota'ma kon pe rɨ iyesi yau, ipokena' kupʉ auya'nokon pɨ', ipʉremasa' pe rɨ ɨwesi kon mɨrɨ. “To' enari'panin ɨyenari'patɨ'nin; ketʉipɨ'tʉu.”\f + \fr 3:14 \ft Aisaya 8:12-13\f*
\v 15 E'tane ɨyewan kon yau Kʉrai inamatɨ' Itepuru pe. Tekonekai' rɨ e'pɨ'tɨ' ɨye'ku'to' kon ekama'popɨ'nin nan ei'nin nan pe ɨwesi kon pa.\x - \xo 3:15 \xt Ma'siu 5:10\x*
\v 16 E'tane iku'tɨ' ɨ'sɨ'mʉn yai mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉnamasen pe, wakʉ pe ɨyewan kon tʉkonekai', mɨrɨ a'tai kamo ɨri pe ɨku'pai'nokon na'ne' nan wakʉ ɨnkupʉnʉ kon Kʉrai yau pɨ' ɨpiyɨ'to' pe ɨri pe ɨpɨ'nokon tʉusauro'sa' kon pɨ'.
\v 17 Wakʉ pe parɨ iyesi ɨyekota'ma kon wakʉ kupʉ auya'nokon wenai, Papa eseru pe iyesi yau, ɨri kupʉ auya'nokon wenai entai.
\p 
\v 18 Apʉne pʉra Kʉrai erikʉ'pʉ\f + \fr 3:18 \fq erikʉ'pʉ, \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra \fq ekota'ma'pʉ\f* amakooi kon wenai tikin ite'kwa, mɨrɨ enta' teri'ton pe pʉra rɨ, ipokena' pe te'san, ipokena' pe te'san pen iwano' pe, ɨne'nin kon pe Papa piya'. Uma'tan nɨto' ya' itʉrʉ'pʉ ipun tau, e'tane nurɨne iyena'pʉ iya'kwarʉ winɨ,
\v 19 kʉrɨ rɨ winɨ rɨ marɨ itɨ'pʉ itekare ekamai' pariki'si tau te'san a'kwarʉ'san piya',
\v 20 pena main awɨrɨ iye'sa' kon pen Papa enuri'tane tʉuseta'kai' pʉra Nowa a'tai'ne a' e'kapʉ koro'tau. Mɨrɨ yau, tu'kan kon pen nɨ, 8 kaisaron kon ka'pon amʉ' epika'tɨ'pʉ tuna yai,\x - \xo 3:20 \xt Iseneses 6:1—7:24\x*
\v 21 serɨ si tuna uya epa'taisiman nɨto' ekamasa', ɨpika'tɨ kon pɨ' na'ne' serɨ pe—ipun utoi'masa' korʉka iya pen e'tane Papa ekama'po wakʉ ɨyewan kon e'sepoto' pe.\f + \fr 3:21 \fq e'tane Papa ekama'po wakʉ ɨyewan kon e'sepoto' pe; \ft mɨrɨ pe pʉra, \fq e'tane epa'taisiman ta esi Papa auro'ka iku'to' pe imaimu awɨrɨ e'nɨto' pe, apʉne pʉra wakʉ pe uyewan kon esi pɨ' iwinɨkʉi' ta e'kwa pe iyesi.\f* Ɨpika'tɨsa' iya 'nokon Sises Kʉrai e'mʉ'sa'kasa' winɨ.
\v 22 Iyenuku'pʉ na'ne' Epʉn pona, mɨrɨpan esi Papa emiyatʉ enwo'netʉ winɨ—inserʉ amʉ', eke ton mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pana'pano ton itena' te'tʉsan pe.
\c 4
\s1 Uko'man Nɨ Papa Iwano' Pe
\p 
\v 1 Mɨrɨ pe si iyesi pɨ', Kʉrai si ekota'ma'pʉ tʉpun yau esi'pʉ na'ne' kasa rɨ marɨ, e'sepaai'tɨtɨ' iteseru rʉ'pʉ ke, apʉne pʉra kʉrɨ rɨ tʉpun yau iyekota'masa' rʉ'pʉ uya makoi nonkasa' mɨrɨ.
\v 2 Mɨrɨ moron nʉ'pʉ pe, serɨ non po si tʉuko'mamʉ koro'tau ka'pon e'to' i'se awɨrɨ iko'mamʉ pen, e'tane nin Papa e'to' i'se awɨrɨ.
\v 3 Apʉne pʉra inke ɨuko'mansa' kon man Papa i'tunin nan pen nʉkupʉnʉ kupʉ pɨ'—ipan pe ɨri kupʉ pɨ' ɨko'manpai e'nɨ pɨ', ɨiwano' kon pen nɨ enkuui pe e'nɨ pɨ', e'taripan pɨ', ipɨ' rɨ te'kamai' e'taripan pɨ' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ekuman pɨ', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨri kuru rɨ nuirapanin nɨ papa tato' ipɨ' pe ika'sa' apurɨpɨtʉ pɨ'.
\v 4 To' pona ti'tupɨ'sen pe pʉra iyesi ta'kɨrɨ'nokon ɨwesi kon kasa pʉra mɨrɨ rɨ marɨ e'ta'nʉ'nɨto' i'mʉnpʉri ka' ɨusenasika kon kasa pʉra, mɨrɨpan kon uya si asapema kon.
\v 5 E'tane si tʉnkupʉ'pʉ kon ekamato' oton to' uya nurɨnan kon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ iyeri'sa' kon eseru aimenkanin pe iye'kamasa' na'ne' ena'.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi wenai, wakʉ itekare usekamasa' na'ne' iyeri'sa' pe rɨ na'ne' nan pɨ', to' eseru aimenkato' pe ka'pon eseru awɨrɨ ipun eseru pɨkɨrɨ, e'tane tʉuko'mansan Papa eseru awɨrɨ iya'kwarʉ pɨkɨrɨ.
\p 
\v 7 Tanporon nɨ u'ma'to' man a'ko pe. Mɨrɨ pe si iyesi pɨ', wakʉ pe ɨusenuminkato' kon yau mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ɨiwano' kon pe tʉuse'se'tɨi' e'tɨ' ɨwɨpʉrema kon pa.
\v 8 Tanporon entai, ɨtonpa kon ti'nʉnkai' ipan pe e'tɨ', apʉne pʉra usi'nʉnkan nɨto' uya tu'kan nɨ makoi nɨpontɨ.\x - \xo 4:8 \xt Ipu'ketʉ 10:12\x*
\v 9 Ɨtonpa kon amʉ' tereutanʉ'se to' a're'tɨtɨ' tentarunse pʉra.
\v 10 Akaisarɨ'nokon iya'kwarʉ nʉtʉrʉ'pʉ ɨyena'nokon apurɨtɨ' tʉron kon pika'tɨ pɨ', iyawɨron pe esii'ma wakʉ nonkasa' Papa uya ɨ'si'taino' nan nɨ tʉrʉ pe.
\v 11 Ɨnʉ' rɨ usaurokʉ pe iyesi yau, tɨwɨ nʉsaurokʉi Papa maimu pe kuru. Ɨnʉ' rɨ esi yau apiyo' pe, tɨwɨ nʉkupʉi Papa nʉtʉrʉ'pʉ tʉmeruntɨrʉ ke, tanporon yau rɨ Papa apurɨpɨ'to' pe Sises Kʉrai poro. Itiwano' pe rɨ eke pe iku'to' nesii mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ipana'pano tɨwɨrɨ rɨ, tɨwɨrɨ rɨ. Amen.
\s1 Ekota'man Kʉri'san Pe E'nɨ Pɨ'
\p 
\v 12 Utonpa ton nʉ'kwɨ, kɨsewansiukatʉu, ɨsɨ rɨ ɨi'tuto' kon yau ɨyekota'ma kon pɨ', ti'tupɨ'sen pen nɨ e'kupʉ kasa rɨ ɨpɨ'nokon.
\v 13 E'tane epori'matɨ' Kʉrai ekota'mato' yau rɨ ɨwesi kon pɨ', mɨrɨ pɨ' mɨrɨ entai ɨyepori'ma kon pa eke pe iku'to' usenpoika a'tai.
\v 14 Asapema kon pe iyesi yau Kʉrai ese' wenai, wakʉ eposa' auya'nokon mɨrɨ, apʉne pʉra iya'kwarʉ eke pe iku'to' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ Papa A'kwarʉ esi pɨ' ɨpo'nokon.
\v 15 Ɨyekota'ma kon pe iyesi yau, te'wɨsen pe ɨwesi kon pɨ' mɨrɨ pe pʉra ama' e' pe, mɨrɨ pe pʉra ti'tui' pʉra rɨ ɨri ku'nin pe, mɨrɨ pe pʉra rɨ ka'pon amʉ' eseru pɨ' rɨ tʉuko'mansen pe ɨwesi kon pɨ' ɨkota'ma kon kʉsemapu'tɨtʉu.
\v 16 E'tane nin, Kʉri'san pe ɨwesi kon pɨ' ɨkota'ma kon yau, kɨpiyɨ'tʉu, e'tane Papa rɨken apurɨpɨ'tɨ' mɨrɨ ese' esa' pe ɨwesi kon pɨ'.
\v 17 Apʉne pʉra eseru aimenkato' weyu si epiya'tɨkapʉ Papa munkɨ pɨ'; iyepiya'tɨ pe si iyesi yau urɨ'nokon pɨ', ɨ'rɨ kasa ken si iye'to' oton kamo wakʉ Papa ekareei awɨron kon pen pɨ'?
\v 18 Mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ,
\q1 “Sa'man pe ipokena' pe te'san epika'tɨ poken pʉra iyesi yau,
\q2 ɨ'rɨ pe ken si Papa uya tasa' pen nɨ awɨrɨ te'san mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉmakooikena' nan e'to' oton?”\f + \fr 4:18 \ft Ipu'ketʉ 11:31\f*
\m tasa'.
\p 
\v 19 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ' ken si, kamoro Papa e'to' i'se pɨkɨrɨ tekota'masan ne'tʉrʉi tʉmaimu awɨron tʉka'nin nʉ'pʉ kon ena' mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ wakʉ kupʉ pɨ' te'to' kon pe miyarɨ rɨ.
\c 5
\s1 Itepuru Ton Mɨrɨ Awonsi'kɨ Moine Ton Enakan
\p 
\v 1 Itepuru ton ɨ'koro'tau'nokon te'san pɨ' ta uya, urɨ itepuru rɨ nɨrɨ, Kʉrai ekota'ma ennin nʉ'pʉ mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ eke pe iku'to' usenpoika a'tai epo ton:
\v 2 Papa ikʉn non ɨyenau'nokon na'ne' nan pa'simanin nan pe e'tɨ', to' ennin pe e'tʉrawasomatɨ'—ayapiyo'ma kon pɨ' pen, e'tane ari'kena' pe ɨwesi kon pɨ' Papa e'to' i'se awɨrɨ; mentaino pe pʉra pʉrata pɨ', e'tane e'tʉrawasomapaino ye' pe;
\v 3 kamoro ɨyena'nokon itʉsa' kon epuru pe ke'ku'tʉu, e'tane wakʉ Papa ikʉn non nenton ku'nin pe.
\v 4 Mɨrɨpan si karimeru amʉ' pa'simanin nan epuru usenpoika a'tai, a'kwa ayarʉkooi kon, kʉron eporo auya'nokon mɨrɨ tenkɨ'sɨimu'nasen pen nɨ.
\p 
\v 5 Moine ton, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ e'tʉtɨ' kɨɨyi' amʉ' ena'. Epontɨtɨ' mɨ pe te'ku'se pʉra e'nɨto' ke ɨtonpa kon amʉ' winɨkʉi', apʉne pʉra,
\q1 “Papa uya mɨ pe te'ku'san ewaruma'tɨ,
\q2 e'tane mɨ pe te'ku'san pen pona wakʉ nonkasa' tʉrʉ iya.”\f + \fr 5:5 \ft Ipu'ketʉ 3:34\f*
\m tasa'.
\v 6 Mɨrɨ pe iyesi pɨ', mɨ pe te'ku'san pe pʉra enatɨ' eke Papa emiya o'no, ayanʉnto' kon pe iya i'se te'to' weyu a'tai.
\v 7 Tanporo rɨ ayanpokʉmanin kon eno'matɨ' itena', apʉne pʉra amainanpanin kon pe iyesi.
\p 
\v 8 Ɨiwano' kon pe tʉuse'se'tɨi', mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tenu ke e'tɨ'. Ɨyeyaton kon, Makoi man tʉyo' tʉnanton warinpa pɨ' rayan kasa.
\v 9 Inurunpatɨ', pana' pe anapurɨnʉ kon yau e'mʉ'sa'katɨ', apʉne pʉra i'tu auya'nokon ɨtonpa kon amʉ' non emʉ' kaisaron kon uya mɨrɨ rɨ marɨ ekota'man nɨto' moronka.
\p 
\v 10 Papa, tanporon nɨ wakʉ nonkasa' esa', ɨkɨ'manin kon nʉ'pʉ tɨwɨro' rɨ a'kwa ya' Kʉrai yau, mara rʉ'kwɨ ɨyekota'ma'pʉ kon tʉpoi si ɨkoneka iya 'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ pana' pe ɨkupʉ iya 'nokon, ayapɨtanʉkʉ iya 'nokon, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ tʉutamasen pe pʉra rɨ ɨkupʉ iya 'nokon.
\p 
\v 11 Tɨwɨ meruntɨ, tɨwɨro' rɨ nesii itenawon pe. Amen.
\s1 Iu'matʉ Pe Rɨ Miyarɨ Tato'
\p 
\v 12 Sairas\f + \fr 5:12 \ft Kiri' \fq Sirʉpanas, Sairas \ft tato' tʉron nɨ pe.\f* uya tʉpika'tɨi', uni'tunʉ, mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ i'napairon utonpa, to'ken nʉ'kwɨ ɨyena'nokon imenuka uya ɨpori'mapɨtʉ uya 'nokon mɨrɨ awonsi'kɨ ekama uya serɨ esi i'napairo' kuru wakʉ nonkasa' Papa uya. Pana' pe iyau e'mʉ'sa'katɨ'.
\v 13 Kʉrɨ Paperan\f + \fr 5:13 \fq Paperan\ft —Isenpoikasa' karetaai yau na'ne' kasa, Ron pɨ' ta iya pe iyesi.\f* po na'ne' anʉnsa' rʉ'pʉ aya'kɨrɨ'nokon uya miyarɨ ta ɨpɨ'nokon, mɨrɨ kasa rɨ marɨ umu, Ma', miyarɨ nɨkayan.\x - \xo 5:13 \xt Inkupʉ'pʉ 12:12, 25; 13:13; 15:37-39; Koro'se 4:10; Pairiman 24\x*
\v 14 Ɨtonpa kon pɨ' miyarɨ ka'tɨ' ɨusi'nʉnka kon pɨ' auta'su'ka kon pe. Usewankaman nɨto' pʉra nesii ɨpiyau'nokon ɨmɨrɨ'nokon Kʉrai yau te'san.
